tftp-hpa (5.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * As of version 5, tftpd-hpa always runs now always as daemon mode,
    it is too error prone and messy to support inetd mode.

  * As of version 5, tftpd-hpa uses now /srv/tftp as server root
    (previously, it was /var/lib/tftpboot).

